@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_elimwt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v1 + 0.27 / v0 + 0.59)))
    v2 = wp.exp(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.98) + wp.exp(0.30))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    tmp = wp.sin((tmp + wp.sin(v1 + 0.84)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.89) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.85)) / 0.41)
    data[tid] = v0
